originalText.text: Great resources for people wanting to model or act. The techniques I learned at the commercial acting class was revolutionary. One of the students had started booking commercials after only 6 classes. This company really knows what they are doing. We went to a casting directors class before and really got nothing out of it but this class was light years ahead of anything we were ever taught.

originalText.text:
We went to a seminar on breaking into the modeling business and also one for how to get into movies. Both were very informative and they had professional models and agents from Ford and Wilhelmina there. At the acting seminar they had casting directors that actually casted for the XMEN and other huge movies. They took headshots and gave us information on how they choose talent.

They really guided us in the right direction and put us in touch with professionals we would never ever get to meet without expect contacts like this.

originalText.text: I went to a commercial modeling class that they give and was blown away by the amount of useful information that was given. This gave me a clear and focused understanding of what I have to do to make it as a model and just how to train myself to be better in front of the camera. It was not as easy as I thought. The people training us are and were real professional super models with so many jobs under their belts my jaw dropped when I had seen their work. I'm totally excited for the first time in my life that I can really do this!

originalText.text: My daughter was trying to become an actress and get into commercials for a while now. We went to one of these classes and she picked up on the teachings right away. She practiced a lot and by the 4th time she was very fluent and could easily do all of the lines using different emotions. Great cources and amazing teachers. Can't wait to go to one of the group events.

originalText.text: Best model information and castings in New York. I went to a 30 Rock seminar where they had the casting director come in and give us all the insite on how to get on the show and then they took our headshots and spoke to everyone about different roles that are coming up.
